  "texts": [
    "Fieblinger et al. [84] proposed a framework to extract CTI from unstructured data sources using LLM automatically.",
    "They employed the guidance framework and QLoRA fine-tuning techniques to guide LLMs in extracting CTI triples from unstructured data and subsequently organizing these triples into the structured and queryable Knowledge Graphs.",
    "The team found that the guidance framework performed better compared to prompt engineering.",
    "Also, incorporating ontology structure and a small number of examples into the prompts improved the quality of the generated CTI triples.",
    "View is a BERTbased threat entity identifier that extracts threat entities from cybersecurity report texts [85]."
  ],
